量,佢都大個仔啦~值唔值得復合,由佢決定啦,我地做左自己個PART就算啦...."},{"pid":"cf562bcea4d1274a63fe856fb874fda78adf1111","tid":1623710,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcfd51f80809bca43d5cf3595efb02727bf1e3da","tid":1623710,"uid":227623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a11fd101fe136f28f4ed54d9234524eed260265e","tid":1623710,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6b95cebaafc60409ac461d2dc9adddd3923c1a1","tid":1623710,"uid":227623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:18:21.000Z","msg":"性格唔啱係佢覺得 <br />\n因為我覺得佢已經唔想維持 所以決定放手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:17:38.000Z","msg":"你地拍左拖幾耐呀？<br />\n有時未必係比唔到新鮮感而分手既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:32:28.000Z","msg":"三個月🥺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"而家點"},{"pid":"bb62e680d98650ebde11309354ba699b6add31e8","tid":1623710,"uid":227623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf562bcea4d1274a63fe856fb874fda78adf1111","tid":1623710,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcfd51f80809bca43d5cf3595efb02727bf1e3da","tid":1623710,"uid":227623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a11fd101fe136f28f4ed54d9234524eed260265e","tid":1623710,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:17:38.000Z","msg":"你地拍左拖幾耐呀？<br />\n有時未必係比唔到新鮮感而分手既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:32:28.000Z","msg":"三個月🥺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"而家點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"分咗手啦"},{"pid":"b6a12f4e138f3af1351ab8bcdc91b07def177bbe","tid":1623710,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb62e680d98650ebde11309354ba699b6add31e8","tid":1623710,"uid":227623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf562bcea4d1274a63fe856fb874fda78adf1111","tid":1623710,"uid":295452,"lik